    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大邪王想要霸占这片美丽的大地，战士们，组建起战队，击退它！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/458428fd22140aa73e26793aa3018eed.avif?t=1733837479\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择可以进化5次的帝国战士们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以选择狼群！通过养狼人，使棋库里越来越多狼。然后通过狼的种族羁绊效果，来达到惊人的战斗力，来碾碎敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里还有疯狂施放魔法弹的法师们！准备好迎接漫天魔法弹的盛宴了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/e09132a20e76c184669dcd9ffbebd8b9.avif?t=1733837479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras_big/e09132a20e76c184669dcd9ffbebd8b9.avif?t=1733837479 width=800 height=314 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >350+不同的独具特色的棋子</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >130+各式各样的宝物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+可对棋子使用的物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5个不同风格的英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18个地图</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/89fcb4783001fdf8e112a934ad52bab1.avif?t=1733837479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras_big/89fcb4783001fdf8e112a934ad52bab1.avif?t=1733837479 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家群：702676048</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：双门工作室</p>",
